snippet.title: Jeremy Lim Music
snippet.description: Jeremy Lim is a Canadian composer and music producer for video games, films, and commercials. Blending the worlds of electronic and acoustic music, he creates a wide range of styles – from dance anthems, to tearful ballads, to grand cinematic scores. His loves for narratives, diverse genres, and cultures afar drive his approach where story comes first.
